## 13. Anti-scope (DO NOT do in this TZ)

- ❌ Do NOT migrate away from `PiDialogService`'s signal-based `DialogRef`. The refactor keeps the signal API.
- ❌ Do NOT switch to Angular Material's `MatDialog` or any third-party dialog lib.
- ❌ Do NOT introduce `persistAcrossNavigation` opt-out — tracked in §7.4 as future TZ.
- ❌ Do NOT split TZ-103 into TZ-103a/b/c — atomic refactor cheaper.
- ❌ Do NOT change `DialogRef` API contract (`.closed` + `.close()`) — backward compatibility contract.
